title: NFL ATL: Week 14 preview
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Week 14 preview
description:
A room full of heroes -- Gregg Rosenthal, Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling and Kevin Patra -- preview all of the Week 14 games.  Don’t miss the gang’s hero picks and predictions.  Also, find out what unlucky team will join the ‘forked’ club. Join the conversation on Twitter: @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
